    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. I have babied this car since day one, and it is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a dream and hasn't given me a single lick of trouble. I'm so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel and enjoy such a smooth, spotless ride. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
