      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast: a truly pristine example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the deep, mirror-like finish of its original factory paint with zero imperfections, chips, or swirls. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear, still retaining that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the nuanced climate controls, functions with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented history of preventative maintenance and a powertrain that delivers smooth, effortless performance. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved time capsule. Complete with all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a spotless service record, it represents the gold standard for its model. Serious inquiries only for this investment-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
