    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in pristine condition inside and out\u2014seriously, not a speck of dust or a scratch to be found. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
