    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with its signature individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS system. This unit has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, ensuring the valvetrain operates with factory precision. The chassis remains structurally flawless with a reinforced rear subframe, while the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw gear synchronization. Power is managed via the variable M differential lock, providing superior traction and corner-exit stability. Every bushing, seal, and suspension component is in peak operating condition, maintaining the original longitudinal and lateral dynamics that define this chassis. This is a mechanically pristine example for the discerning collector who values technical integrity and a linear power delivery.",
